      <LongDescription>The &lt;noparse&gt;SGM-H-300 Peck ASM&lt;/noparse&gt; is a size 3 waypoint-capable cruise missile.  It is based on the SGM-H-3 body, which is a high speed hybrid missile designed to strike heavy targets.  This missile will deliver a Contact Fuze, High Explosive, Shaped warhead.  It homes in on its target using an Active Radar seeker, validating that it is the correct target using command guidance from its launching ship.

