      <LongDescription>The &lt;noparse&gt;SDM-227 Gale ACM&lt;/noparse&gt; is a size 2 direct guidance missile.  It is based on the SDM-2 body, which is a flexible defensive missile with a booster.  This missile will deliver a Proximity Fuze, High Explosive, Blast Fragmentation warhead.  It homes in on its target using command guidance from its launching ship.  If the primary seeker does not find a target or is jammed, it can fall back on a Passive Wake seeker.

