      <LongDescription>The &lt;noparse&gt;SGM-H-316 Rending Claw - A&lt;/noparse&gt; is a size 3 waypoint-capable cruise missile.  It is based on the SGM-H-3 body, which is a high speed hybrid missile designed to strike heavy targets.  This missile will deliver a Delayed Contact Fuze, High Explosive, Kinetic Penetrator warhead.  It homes in on its target using command guidance from its launching ship.  If the primary seeker does not find a target or is jammed, it can fall back on a Radar Anti-Radiation seeker.

