      <LongDescription>The &lt;noparse&gt;SGM-265 Roadkill&lt;/noparse&gt; is a size 2 direct guidance missile.  It is based on the SGM-2 body, which is a flexible mainstay anti-ship missile.  This missile will deliver a Contact Fuze, High Explosive, Shaped warhead.  It homes in on its target using an Active Radar seeker, validating that it is the correct target using command guidance from its launching ship.

