      <Description>$MISSILEGUIDANCE_MODE_DIRECT - &lt;color=#D3D11F&gt;$MISSILESEEKER_MODE_COMMAND_ABBREV&lt;/color&gt;/$MISSILESEEKER_MODE_PASSIVE_ABBREV(&lt;color=#D4211D&gt;WAKE&lt;/color&gt;) - $MISSILEWARHEAD_SHORT_BLASTFRAG</Description>
      <LongDescription>The &lt;noparse&gt;SGM-H-35 Squall ACM&lt;/noparse&gt; is a size 3 direct guidance missile.  It is based on the SGM-H-3 body, which is a high speed hybrid missile designed to strike heavy targets.  This missile will deliver a $MISSILEWARHEAD_DETAIL_BLASTFRAG warhead.  It homes in on its target using command guidance from its launching ship  If the primary seeker does not find a target or is jammed, it can fall back on a Passive Wake seeker.

$MISSILESTAT_CONTROLMETHOD: $MISSILEGUIDANCE_MODE_DIRECT
$MISSILESTAT_TARGETINGMODE: &lt;b&gt;&lt;color=#3BC81E&gt;$MISSILESTAT_TARGETINGMODE_POS&lt;/color&gt;	&lt;color=#3BC81E&gt;$MISSILESTAT_TARGETINGMODE_TRACK&lt;/color&gt;&lt;/b&gt;

