      <LongDescription>The &lt;noparse&gt;SGM-H-316 Rending Claw - C&lt;/noparse&gt; is a size 3 waypoint-capable cruise missile.  It is based on the SGM-H-3 body, which is a high speed hybrid missile designed to strike heavy targets.  This missile will deliver a $MISSILEWARHEAD_DETAIL_HEKP warhead.  It homes in on its target using command guidance from its launching ship  If the primary seeker does not find a target or is jammed, it can fall back on a Radar Home-on-Jam seeker.

